msgid ""
"\n"
"    a data project by Robin Hawkes about wasted wind energy in Great "
"Britain. I am grateful for that work as a model for explaining curtailed "
"renewables in a clear, public-facing way.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:179
msgid "About"
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:181
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I built Wasted Sun as a individual that cares about this with the "
"objective of putting unused solar into plain sight. \n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:186
